*cdemu-daemon-3.0.2 (21 Feb 2015)

  21 Feb 2015; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -cdemu-daemon-2.1.0.ebuild, cdemu-daemon-2.1.1.ebuild,
  +cdemu-daemon-3.0.2.ebuild,
  -files/cdemu-daemon-2.1.0-DISABLE_DEPRECATED.patch:
  Version bump, adds image writing (bug #518590, thanks to Rafał Mużyło).
  Drop old.

  26 Jan 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> cdemu-daemon-2.1.1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #494802

  19 Jan 2014; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> cdemu-daemon-2.1.1.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug 494802

